static
string
throw_error
string $message;,integer $error_level=E_USER_NOTICE
This method lets you to trigger customs user errors even if you have not instantiated object.
$error_level can be :
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;256 => 'E_USER_ERROR'
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;512 => 'E_USER_WARNING'
&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1024 => 'E_USER_NOTICE'

